        <p>
		Students will be able to explore the beauty behind physics mechanics. This course is designed for students with a strong mathematical backgrounds who want to get a jump start in their science education. This course will go over the fundamental Physics Mechanics principles in a fun and immersive experience. The curriculum will focus on building an intiution for general concepts while teaching various subjects that will be relevant in preparation for sections of the SAT II Physics and AP Physics C - Mechanics exam.
